Who We Are

Meet Our Team
Driven to Get Results
Applying for benefits can be a difficult undertaking in itself, and attempting
	 to appeal a denial of benefits can be even more complex. You need experienced
	 counsel to obtain your benefits. At ERISA Law Center, we have successfully
	 helped hundreds of persons to get the benefits they deserve under the
	 Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974 (ERISA). This federal
	 law grants employees the right to sue for benefits and breaches of fiduciary
	 duty in regard to pensions and health plan benefits.
Our team is our greatest resource in helping you obtain disability or life
	 insurance benefits. Each member is devoted to serving our clients with
	 courtesy, professionalism, and knowledge. ERISA Attorney Robert Rosati
	 is admitted to practice in over 25 Federal courts around the country.
	 Our team’s focus is to relieve you of the pressure of dealing with
	 insurance company personnel. Through a combination of legal knowledge
	 and commitment, we work single-mindedly toward the best possible result for you.
At ERISA Law Center, our team-centered approach puts your case in the hands
	 of trained professionals every step of the way. Whether it’s in
	 monitoring the insurance company’s performance, appealing denied
	 or terminated benefits or litigating wrongful ERISA benefit denials, our
	 staff will give you the ability to return to your number one task: taking
	 care of yourself and your family.
When you hire ERISA Law Center to handle your ERISA appeal, you are assured
	 of receiving dependable counsel, reasonable fees and the benefits of years
	 of experience.
Our ERISA attorney and support staff are here to relieve you of the pressures
	 often felt when dealing with adjusters and insurance company personnel.
	 With decades of combined experience, we are committed to helping you work
	 toward the most advantageous outcome for your case. Learn more about our
	 team by clicking on the individual bios below.






