What We Do



What We Do

Disability Claim Appeals
If your disability claim was denied, or if you received a letter stating
	 that your existing benefits were terminated, ERISA Law Center can help.
	 Do not lose hope in this situation, as in many cases you can file a successful
	 ERISA claim appeal. An appeal gives you the opportunity to overturn the
	 initial decision, and it is a required step under ERISA legal procedure
	 before you can proceed with a lawsuit against your disability insurance company.

Read more
about disability claim appeals.









