California ERISA Attorney
Let Our Results-Driven Lawyer Help
Our mission at ERISA Law Center is to ensure people get the disability
	 benefits they deserve. If your claim was denied or your existing benefits
	 were terminated, we can help. Employee Retirement Income Security Act
	 (ERISA) claims and litigation can be complicated. Make sure you have an
	 experienced California ERISA lawyer there to help you get the benefits
	 and compensation you need.
We can help with the following:

Appealing a claim
Suing over a claim
Disability claim appeals
Life insurance claims
Long-term disability
Litigating a claim

We Are Ready to Fight for You
Our firm is admitted to practice in numerous federal courts, and we have
	 experience assisting hundreds of people across the nation. Each member
	 of our team is devoted to providing the best service possible, treating
	 our clients with courtesy and professionalism. Our ERISA attorney, Robert
	 Rosati, is able to practice in more than 25 federal courts around the
	 country. Through legal knowledge and commitment, our approach puts your
	 case in the hands of trained professionals.
Who We Fight

	There are a small number of insurance companies and self-insured plans
	 that provide the vast majority of ERISA disability benefits claims. It
	 can also be difficult to deal with them without legal experience, as different
	 insurance companies will take different tactics to try to avoid paying
	 benefits. Some companies react to case law and court decisions and trends
	 in the circuit in order to increase their chances of winning. Take a look at the
	list of insurance companies we’ve come up against.


	If you’re ready to discuss your situation,
	contact us at (844) 710-2993 or fill out our online form. We’re available 24/7.








